                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 1: Do I need an account to buy a pet?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                Yes. You need to create an account to make a purchase. Having an account lets us verify buyers, 
                ensure secure transactions, and provide you with updates about your order.
            </p>

